'''瑞贝卡·芮妮·布莱克'''（{{lang-en|Rebecca Renee Black}}，{{bd|1997年|6月21日|catIdx=Black, Rebecca}}），是[[美国|美国]][[少年流行曲|少年流行曲]]歌手，以其在2011年在{{link-en|ARK音乐工厂|ARK Music Factory}}旗下发布的单曲“[[Friday_(瑞贝卡·布莱克)|Friday]]”一炮走红。该曲在评论界受到恶评，被许多音乐评论家和听众称为是“史上最差的歌曲”。<ref>{{cite news |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/12784330 |last=Whitworth |first=Dan |title='Worst song ever' gets 29m views after going viral |date=21 March 2011 |accessdate=2 April 2011 |archive-date=2011-05-27 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5z0HrwagD?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/12784330 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/chatter/2011/03/rebecca-black-teen-singer-admits-she-cried-when-her-hit-song-was-deemed-worst-song-ever.html?cid=6a00d8341c630a53ef014e5ff8c4bc970c |last=Pierce |first=Tony |title=Rebecca Black, teen singer, admits she cried when her hit song was deemed 'Worst Song Ever' |date=18 March 2011 |accessdate=2 April 2011 |work=[[洛杉矶时报|Los Angeles Times]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110322153132/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/chatter/2011/03/rebecca-black-teen-singer-admits-she-cried-when-her-hit-song-was-deemed-worst-song-ever.html?cid=6a00d8341c630a53ef014e5ff8c4bc970c |archivedate=2011年3月22日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2011/03/22/3170156.htm |title='Worst song ever' tops 30 million views |date=22 March 2011 |accessdate=2 April 2011 |publisher=ABC News Australia |author=[[法新社|AFP]] |archive-date=2011-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110630044120/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2011/03/22/3170156.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>该歌曲的[[音乐录影带|音乐录影带]]在上传至[[YouTube|YouTube]]后，以极快的速度在网络上传播，而这一[[网络迷因|网络迷因]]的主角布莱克也因此备受关注。<ref>{{cite news|url =http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/g/a/2011/04/01/businessinsider-top-viral-videos-of-the-week-2-2011-4.DTL|title =Top Viral Videos of the Week: Rebecca Black 'Friday'|last =Wei|first =William|work =[[旧金山论坛报|San Francisco Chronicle]]|publisher =Hearst Corporation|date =2011-04-01|accessdate =2011-04-04}}</ref>根据[[Google|Google]]时代精神年度盘点，布莱克成为2011年度搜索最多的关键词。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.googlezeitgeist.com/en |title=Google Zeitgeist 2011 |publisher=Google |year=2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120605042426/http://www.googlezeitgeist.com/en |archivedate=2012-06-05 }}</ref>

== 生平 ==
瑞贝卡·布莱克出生在加州安那翰山的社区中。<ref name=ocr>{{cite news|url=http://articles.ocregister.com/2011-03-17/news/29143204_1_music-video-history-of-pop-music-song-and-video|first=Peter|last=Larsen|title=O.C.'s Rebecca Black Talks About Friday|newspaper=The Orange County Register|publisher=[[Freedom_Communications|Freedom Communications]]|date=2011-03-17|accessdate=2011-03-26|archive-date=2013-07-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6I3y4l6WZ?url=http://www.ocregister.com/entertainment/-292662--.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>其父为约翰·布莱克（John Black），其母为乔治娜·马奎斯·凯利（Georgina Marquez Kelly），两人都是[[兽医|兽医]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.oregonlive.com/music/index.ssf/2011/03/as_friday_finally_fades_a_look.html|title=As 'Friday' finally fades, a look back at an old little meme|last=Hall|first=Stan|newspaper=The Oregonian|publisher=Advance Publications|date=2011-03-25|accessdate=2011-03-28|archive-date=2011-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110429090519/http://www.oregonlive.com/music/index.ssf/2011/03/as_friday_finally_fades_a_look.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ny">{{cite news|url=http://parenting.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/03/25/an-internet-stars-mom-responds/|title=An Internet Star's Mom Responds|last=Belkin|first=Lisa|newspaper=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|publisher=The New York Times Company|date=2011-03-25|accessdate=2011-03-28|archive-date=2012-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120120133941/http://parenting.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/03/25/an-internet-stars-mom-responds/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在学校中，布莱克学习舞蹈，参加学校演出的面试，参加音乐夏令营，并在2008年加入爱国教育机构欢聚美国（Celebration USA）后开始公开演唱。<ref name=ocr/>

2010年末，布莱克的一位同学，同时也是[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]{{link-en|ARK音乐工厂|ARK Music Factory}}的客户，向她提起了这个公司。<ref name="Beast">{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/blogs-and-stories/2011-03-17/rebecca-black-friday-and-cyberbullying/|title=Rebecca Black: 'I'm Being Cyberbullied'|last=Lee|first=Chris|date=2011-03-17|work=''The Daily Beast''|publisher=The Newsweek Daily Beast Company|accessdate=2011-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110318141406/http://www.thedailybeast.com/blogs-and-stories/2011-03-17/rebecca-black-friday-and-cyberbullying/|archive-date=2011-03-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>布莱克的母亲支付4000美元，由ARK音乐工厂为她的女儿打造一部音乐录影带，并且布莱克家拥有该录音带的母带。<ref name="ny"/>于是，布莱克的单曲“Friday”问世并登陆[[Youtube|Youtube]]和[[iTunes|iTunes]]。在YouTube上的影片上传于2011年2月10日，在首月只有大约1000人次收看。<ref name=ocr/>到了2011年3月11日（星期五），该影片迅速走红，在几日内获得了百萬點閱量，并且登上[[社交网络|社交网络]]站点[[Twitter|Twitter]]的热门话题榜首，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.smh.com.au/technology/technology-news/who-is-rebecca-black-and-is-she-really-bigger-than-japan-20110315-1bvkj.html|accessdate=2011-03-24|date=2011-03-15|first=Lee-Maree|last=Gello|title=Rebecca Black Friday Song Is Top Twitter Trending Topic Youtube|newspaper=The Sydney Morning Herald]publisher =Fairfax Media|archive-date=2011-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110318172904/http://www.smh.com.au/technology/technology-news/who-is-rebecca-black-and-is-she-really-bigger-than-japan-20110315-1bvkj.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>并在媒体上恶评如潮。<ref>{{cite web|url =http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/why-rebecca-blacks-much-mocked-viral-hit-friday-is-actually-good-20110315|title =Why Rebecca Black's Much Mocked Viral Hit Is Actually Good|last =Perpetua|first =Matthew|work =[[滚石|Rolling Stone]]|publisher =Wenner Media|date =2011-03-15|accessdate =2011-03-28|archive-date =2012-02-04|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20120204233731/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/why-rebecca-blacks-much-mocked-viral-hit-friday-is-actually-good-20110315|dead-url =no}}</ref>截至2011年5月14日，该影片在YouTube上的评分为456,334票喜欢，3,213,240票不喜欢。而且由於劣評如潮，該影片上傳者已停用該影片的評論功能。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CD2LRROpph0 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-04-08 |archive-date=2011-06-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5zId7qrzY?url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CD2LRROpph0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而截至2011年3月22日，其数字单曲首周销量为40,000份，<ref name="bb">{{cite web|url =http://www.billboard.com/news/rebecca-black-s-friday-first-week-sales-1005084932.story|title =Rebecca Black's First Week Sales High But Not In Millions|last =Peoples|first =Glen|work =Billboard|publisher =Prometheus Global Media|date =2011-03-22|accessdate =2011-03-28|archive-date =2011-11-26|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20111126150456/http://www.billboard.com/news/rebecca-black-s-friday-first-week-sales-1005084932.story|dead-url =no}}</ref>而在iTunes上则有超过百万的下载量，为其赚得超过850,000英镑的收入。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/music/3484368/Rebecca-is-in-the-Black.html|title=Rebecca is in the Black|publisher=The Sun|date= 2011-03-02}}</ref>在[[公告牌百强单曲榜|公告牌百强单曲榜]]上，该曲最高位列第58位，在新西兰单曲榜上则最高达到第33位。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/news/lady-gaga-glee-songs-dominate-hot-100-1005089442.story|title=Lady Gaga, 'Glee' Songs Dominate Hot 100|date=2011-03-23|first=Gary|last=Trust|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|location=New York|accessdate=2011-02-23|archive-date=2011-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110326024610/http://www.billboard.com/news/lady-gaga-glee-songs-dominate-hot-100-1005089442.story|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="newzealand">{{cite web|url=http://www.charts.org.nz/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Rebecca+Black|title=Rebecca Black – Friday|work=''Charts.org.nz''|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=2011-03-23|archive-date=2012-07-27|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69SSmQBgt?url=http://www.charts.org.nz/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Rebecca+Black|dead-url=no}}</ref>在英国，该曲发布伊始排名第61位。<ref name="UKcharts"/>

3月25日，布莱克已经雇佣了一名公共推广师和一名经纪人。而她的经纪人证实，已经有部分作曲家和厂牌有意为布莱克创作新歌，并制作专辑。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/news/rebecca-black-looks-to-move-beyond-friday-1005093722.story|title=Rebecca Black Looks To Move Beyond 'Friday'|date=March 25, 2011|first=Gail|last=Mitchell|first2=Glenn|last2=Peoples|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|location=New York|accessdate=2011-03-27|archive-date=2011-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110913123739/http://www.billboard.com/news/rebecca-black-looks-to-move-beyond-friday-1005093722.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>在接受英国《太阳报》的采访中，布莱克表示自己将录制一首名为《LOL》的新歌，并且还在筹划新专辑 。<ref name="nme"/>她表示自己目前并没有签约，而她的专辑也会有和“Friday”主题相同的歌曲。<ref name="nme">{{cite web|url =http://www.nme.com/news/various-artists/55718|title =Rebecca Black following 'Friday' with 'LOL' single and album|work =[[NME|New Musical Express]]|publisher =Time Inc.|date =2011-03-26|accessdate =2011-03-28|archive-date =2016-04-18|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160418104609/http://www.nme.com/news/various-artists/55718|dead-url =no}}</ref>另外，布莱克客串演出凱蒂·佩芮單曲《Last Friday Night (T.G.I.F.)》的音樂錄像帶。

2011年7月18日，布莱克通过[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]发行了她的第二支单曲《[[My_Moment|My Moment]]》，作为对之前恶评《Friday》者的回应，该曲的音乐录音带也被上传到[[Youtube|Youtube]]上。据称，她将在8月发行一张有5首歌曲的[[迷你专辑|迷你专辑]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/news#/news/rebecca-black-to-self-release-new-single-1005270572.story |title=''Billboard:'' Rebecca Black to Self-Release New Single 'My Moment,' EP  |accessdate=2011-04-08 |archive-date=2010-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101130200342/http://www.billboard.com/news#/news/rebecca-black-to-self-release-new-single-1005270572.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>
